<item>
            <title>[PIG-475] &quot;task failed to report status&quot; error</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-475</link>
                <project id="12310730" key="PIG">Pig</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When running a very large query a user got the following error after 90 minutes:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;org.apache.pig.backend.hadoop.executionengine.mapReduceLayer.Launcher&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;gt;&amp;gt; - Error message from task (reduce) tip_200810072143_0004_r_000033Task&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;gt;&amp;gt; task_200810072143_0004_r_000033_0 failed to report status for 600 &lt;br/&gt;
&amp;gt;&amp;gt; seconds. Killing!&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Looks like we missed reporting progress in a few places.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
