                            <comment id="12638004" author="shravanmn" created="Wed, 8 Oct 2008 17:53:28 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The query that cause the error will be helpful than generally looking around where we missed it and it might be that there is a udf which doesn&apos;t do reporting. Could you pls attach the script?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12638665" author="shravanmn" created="Fri, 10 Oct 2008 22:33:37 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The PhysicalOperator.reporter initialization in PigMapReduce.Reduce.reduce was missing&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12638692" author="olgan" created="Sat, 11 Oct 2008 00:25:49 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;patch committed; thanks shravan!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12682743" author="vzaliva" created="Tue, 17 Mar 2009 18:17:36 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I am using SVN trunk version (checked out March 16, 2009) and getting these errors on one of my pig scripts.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Task attempt_200903131720_0047_m_000270_0 failed to report status for 627 seconds. Killing!&lt;br/&gt;
...&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I could not successfully complete this task even once!&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This task is working with data in bz2 format. My other tasks are working with non-bz2 data. Maybe this is a reason?&lt;/p&gt;
</comment>
